headline: Nasdaq (NDAQ): Buy, Sell, or Hold Post Q2 Earnings?
summary: While the S&P 500 is up 24.7% since April 2025, Nasdaq (currently trading at $87.45 per share) has lagged behind, posting a return of 18.5%. This might have investors contemplating their next move.
